These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, singing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | gardening | card-games | singing   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
House: cape-cod, modern, farmhouse
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the modern house is on the far left##1
3. the modern house is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| House   | modern | cape-cod | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff, bolivar
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Cigar       | cain     | davidoff | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, satire
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Movie-Genre    | satire    | martial-arts     | thriller |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, milk
1. the person drinking cola is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Beverage   | milk        | sprite | cola    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, amber, fuchsia
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Color        | fuchsia | grey      | amber  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
