3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing go is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Game   | scrabble      | billiard     | go    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

