2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person eating peach is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | animation | time-travel |

