.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, aconite
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| Flower   | daisy | lily | aconite |

