There 3 different types of food: spinach, pomegranate, zucchini
1. the fan of metal is in the middle##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal     | reggae   |
| Food   | pomegranate | spinach | zucchini |

