.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, rowing
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, lawyer, pilot
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Sport   | surfing | baseball | rowing    |
| Job        | coach    | pilot | lawyer |

