.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
House: futuristic, palace, townhouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the palace house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| House    | townhouse | futuristic       | palace  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 